item.description: Jason Tartick reflected on his relationship with Kaitlyn Bristowe in his new book, Talk Money to Me, saying they “never had a candid conversation” about money before moving in together. item.description: Rom-com king Hugh Grant has certainly had something of a roller coaster of a love life. In the 1990s, he was all loved up with theseemingly ageless actress Liz Hurley (whom he said had the best pair around). Then in 1995, he was caught in Los Angeles with working girl Divine Brown. They hung in there for a while, but ultimately it was bye-bye Liz. Fast forward to 2011 and the 51-year-old Grant ups and has a daughter named Tabitha with a Chinese woman named Tinglan Hong.

item.title: Tribeca Film Festival 2023 Lineup, Location And Ticket Details
item.description: Tribeca film festival 2023 lineup is divided into Feature, Short, and Immersive films. Tribeca Now and Audio Storytelling are based on streaming and broadcasts. Organized by Tribeca Productions, the annual film festival showcases a diverse selection of films, talks, music, games, art, episodic, immersive programming, audio storytelling, TV, and XR. It was founded by Robert De Niro, Craig Hatkoff, and Jane Rosenthal in 2001 to prompt economic and cultural revitalization of lower Manhattan after the terrifying September 11 attacks on the World Trade Center.

item.title: Catherine Kassenoff Obituary: What Happened To Her?
item.description: Recently, Catherine Kassenoff has drawn astonishment and grief because of her story, which highlights the challenges parents experience when battling for custody in the family court system.  She worked as a federal prosecutor before becoming an activist for family court reform. item.title: Padma Lakshmi Details Her Reasons for Leaving 'Top Chef'
item.description: Padma Lakshmi opened up about her reasons for leaving Top Chef after hosting the Bravo competition series for 17 years. Lakshmi, 52, detailed her thought process in an interview with Variety’s “Awards Circuit” podcast on Thursday, August 24. “I had been on location for eight months out of the year. And when I wasn’t on location, I was in pre- and post-production for both my shows,” she explained, referring to Top Chef and her Hulu series, Taste the Nation.

item.title: Patricia Southall Bio, Wiki, Age, Husband, Daughter, Family, Treasure You, Miss Virginia, Net Worth.
item.description: Patricia Southall Biography Patricia Southall is a renowned American founder and spokesperson of Treasure You, ex-wife of comedian Martin Lawrence and the wife of former Dallas Cowboys running back and Pro Football Hall of Famer Emmitt Smith. The former beauty queen from Chesapeake, Virginia is a James Madison University journalism graduate who won the Miss Virginia USA crown in late 1993. Representing Virginia in the Miss USA 1994 pageant, Patricia placed first runner-up to Lu Parker of South Carolina.

item.title: Raheem Mostert Restructures Contract With 49ers, Can Earn Up To $5 Million In 2020
item.description: Earlier this month, San Francisco 49ers running back Raheem Mostert requested a trade after the two sides failed to agree on a new contract. But on Monday, the 49ers agreed to give their 2019 playoff hero a new deal that includes several incentives. According to NFL Network's Tom Pelissero, Mostert's new contract includes a $250,000 signing bonus. With incentives, he can make up to $5 million in the upcoming 2020 season.

item.title: Where Is Sally Mcneil Now? Insights About The Netflix Documentary Killer Sally
item.description: Where is Sally Mcneil now? After the trailer of the three-part documentary Killer Sally, the internet is flooded with users who are curious to know about her and where is Sally Mcneil now. The documentary Killer Sally has three parts. The first part is based on Sally’s abusive childhood at her home, the second part revolves around her romantic life with her husband, Ray Mcneil. However, things took an ugly turn in the third part.

item.title: WWE Already Replaces CM Punk in the WrestleMania 30 Poster, British Celeb Attends Impact Tapings, Ja
item.description: WWE Already Replaces CM Punk in WrestleMania 30 Poster In what looks to be an even further sign that WWE might not have any plans to try and bring CM Punk back to the company in time for WrestleMania 30, the company has replaced him on the official WrestleMania promo poster with the 'Mania logo. The poster now features John Cena, Mark Henry, Brock Lesnar, The Undertaker, Alberto Del Rio and Randy Orton, and Punk has been cropped out.

item.title: Beyonce Shows Footage Losing Star Search in "Flawless" Music Video
item.description: She may be Queen Bey now, but 20 years ago, Beyonce and her Houston, Texas-based hip hop group Girl’s Tyme weren’t considered winners by the Star Search judges. In the “Flawless” music video on her new record-breaking visual album, Beyonce shares footage of the girl group losing to the rockers Skeleton Crew back in 1993.  Girl’s Tyme was managed by Beyonce’s father Mathew Knowles before later becoming hit groupDestiny’s Child. In the clip, the Star Search announcer Ed McMahon introduces them as “Beyonce, LaTavia, Nina, Nikki, Kelly and Ashley, the hip-hop rappin’ Girl’s Tyme!

item.title: Catherine O'Hara Recalls Being Mistaken for Macaulay Culkins Mom
item.description: Catherine O’Hara may have played Macaulay Culkin’s mom in the Home Alone movies, but she is not his mother in real life — a fact people sometimes forget. The actress, 69, told Sunday TODAY on Thursday, February 8, that Culkin, 43 asked her to present his award at the Hollywood Walk of Fame ceremony in Los Angeles in December 2023, noting that she was honored to be invited by her onscreen son to attend.

item.title: Ice hockey action coming to Truist Field this week WSOC TV
item.description: CHARLOTTE — Something cool is coming to Truist Field this week. For the first time, the Charlotte Knights will host ice hockey on the ballpark’s newly installed, regulation-sized ice rink in the outfield. Up first is the Charlotte Rush, a Tier III junior hockey program in the United States Premier Hockey League, who will host the Carolina Junior Hurricanes on Friday. The action will begin at 4:30 p.m., with the Charlotte Rush Elite team taking on the Carolina Junior Hurricanes Elite team.

Karrueche Tran Defends Selling Feet Pics On Only Fans
item.description: Karrueche Tran recently spoke out after fans discovered that she was selling pictures of her feet on the private subscription site, OnlyFans. Critics began making claims that the model and actress’ latest venture was due to her “going broke,” to which she set the record straight. “LOL at all the comments regarding OF,” she wrote in a since-deleted tweet on Tuesday (Mar. 12). “I’m not going broke.. just a smart play.

item.title: Dunkin' Is Selling Lip Balm That Looks Like Munchkins
item.description: Dunkin’ (formerly Dunkin’ Donuts) is here for all your beauty needs! The Massachusetts-based chain recently debuted a line of lip balms, and although the restaurant has surprisingly released some lip products before, this is a brand-new batch. The product, which appears to have hit the market earlier this month, is sold as a set of two. Each of the egg-shaped lip balms are meant to look like Munchkins, and the duo of beauty products even come in a box designed to resemble the square container that Dunkin’s beloved doughnut holes are sold in.

As the global protein supplement market grows to an expected USD 31.4 billion by 2027, it’s worth seeking out cleaner options that align with your health goals.

item.title: Ariana Grande To Match $1.5 Million In Donations To Fight Anti-Trans Bills
item.description: Ariana Grande is the latest celebrity to use her platform to take a stand against the rise of anti-transgender legislation across the United States. But more than just speaking out, the singer has pledged to match up to $1.5 million in donations to 18 separate LGBTQ+ organizations to support their advocacy. Sharing with her 303 million Instagram followers, Grande made a post in honor of Transgender Day of Visibility.

item.title: Dallas Cowboys Hire Mike McCarthy As Their New Head Coach
item.description: One week after their season ended in bitter disappointment -- and a day after moving on from Jason Garrett --  the Dallas Cowboys have found a new head coach. On Monday morning, Jay Glazer of Fox Sports reported that the Cowboys have hired Mike McCarthy has their new head coach. ESPN's Todd Archer added that the deal was for five years. McCarthy is the ninth head coach in Cowboys history.

item.title: Jermaine Dupri Reacts to Memes About His Super Bowl Outfit
item.description: When Jermaine Dupri changed into his Super Bowl halftime performance outfit on Sunday, February 11, he never could have predicted the internet’s response. Dupri, 51, joined Usher onstage in a cropped black and white suit. As he introduced Usher’s 2004 song “Confessions” (which appears on the titular album that Dupri produced), viewers couldn’t help but notice the pair of thick white socks that poked out from his chunky black loafers.

item.title: Kandi Burruss and More 'RHOA' Stars on Potential Casting Change
item.description: The Real Housewives of Atlanta women have some ideas on casting changes for the next season of the Bravo show. Kandi Burruss, who has starred on RHOA since 2009, exclusively told Us Weekly she’s hesitant to add — or even remove — any cast members. “I guess there could be [a shakeup], but every time they decide they want to change people, it’s like, sometimes I’m sad when the people leave that they switched out,” Kandi, 47, said on the BravoCon red carpet in Las Vegas on Saturday, November 4.

item.title: See the Worlds Most Expensive Ugly Christmas Sweater: Pic
item.description: An ugly sweater for a pretty penny. Gone are the days of thrifting to find the perfect top for your ugly Christmas sweater parties. In fact, the garish knitwear is getting more luxurious each and every year, with Tipsy Elves’ World’s Most Expensive Ugly Christmas Sweater taking the cake. The brand teamed with Swarovski to create a top valued at $30,000. If you have that kind of money laying around, the shirt is up for grabs at that same price.

item.description: The rumor mill is going crazy with allegations that O.J. Simpson is claiming to be the biological father of Khloe Kardashian—even going to the length of putting her in his will. In this bizarre report, The National Enquirer suggests that a source confirmed O.J.’s belief that Khloe was birthed through an affair with Kris Jenner while she was still married to her now-deceased husband Robert Kardashian. item.title: Jason Ritters Ups and Downs: Dad John Ritter's Death and More
item.description: Honest about his ups and downs. Jason Ritter has celebrated his triumphs and been candid about his shortcomings over the years. During a March 2023 appearance on The Drew Barrymore Show, the Raise Your Voice actor moved his wife, Melanie Lynskey, to tears by opening up about how his struggles with alcoholism affected the early stages of their romance. “I knew how incredible Melanie was early on,” the Joan of Arcadia alum told host Drew Barrymore when she asked about the moment he knew the Last of Us actress was The One.

The novel, which is set to release on September 24, discusses how the network reinvented itself into a “powerhouse tween network” after letting the stars of their Mickey Mouse Club revival – Britney Spears, Justin Timberlake, Christina Aguilera, Ryan Gosling and more – slip through their fingertips.

item.title: Queen Elizabeth's Coffin Adorned by Orb and Sceptre: Details
item.description: Symbolic artifacts. The late Queen Elizabeth II will lie in state at Westminster Hall from Wednesday, September 14, until her funeral on Monday, September, 19 — and her closed coffin will be adorned with items from the royal family’s Crown Jewel collection. The Sovereign’s Orb and the Sovereign’s Sceptre With Cross will be placed on top of the casket. The orb is presented to British monarchs during their coronation. Dating back to Charles II’s coronation in 1661, the piece of regalia is golden and has a cross perched on top to symbolize heavenly power over the world.
